name: Custom Birthday Outfit - Onsie, Hat and Tutu
description:
1st Birthday Custom Outfit Set

This set includes 1 x tutu, 1 x onsie and 1 x party hat. Included in the price is name and birthday age on both hat and onsie and one themed applique on the back of the onsie. 

This item is made to order and there is a 4 week turnaround time. Available in a onsie from sizes 0000-1 or in a white t-shirt for sizes 2+. Can be customized to your needs for colours, name and number, Please contact us via the contact tab once payment has been processed with the birthday age, name and theme. Colour and applique samples will be emailed across within 24 hours to for approval.

name: Hungry Caterpillar Change Mat
description:
This is not a licensed product. It is however, hand-crafted from licensed fabric. I am not affiliated with or sponsored by Eric Carle Studios.

This cute little change mat teams 100% cotton 'Hungry Caterpillar' themed fabric on the top with a coordinating white flannelette on the bottom. The mat also has a waterproof middle layer to make nappy changing easy and clean. Can be rolled up and snapped together for easy portability.

name: Ballerina Tutu
description:
The perfect outfit for your little prima ballerina!

These tutu's are made to order and can be made in pink or black (if you would like another colour please use the contact tab to message us and we will do our best to accommodate!)

The tutu's can be adorned with a flower as shown in the picture or with your child's first initial (by applique). To have your child's full first name on the leotard please message us to open a custom spot for you, a full name is $5.00 extra. Tutu is fully detachable from leotard. 

Please allow up to four weeks for delivery as this is made to order. Tutu can be made in sizes 3 - 6. . 

Please note your preferred size and if you would like a flower or a letter at time of checkout (please also state childs first initial if you opt for the letter)

name: Once Upon a Time Girls Pram Bassinet Blanket
description:
Girls Fairytale Pram Blanket

Girls pram blanket, teaming a front layer of 100% cotton themed 'Fairytale' fabric with a coordinating back layer of 100% cotton fabric. Blanket also has a light 100% cotton wadding for extra comfort. Light enough to be used all through Summer but still warm enough to keep those chills away. Perfect for the little princess in your life and will also make a great gift.

name: Dinosaur Change Mat
description: This super soft and comfy change mat teams 100% cotton 'Dinosaur' themed fabric on the top with a coordinating white flannelette on the bottom. The mat also has a middle layer of batting to make it super soft and comfy for your baby to lay on.

name: Unisex Hungry Caterpillar Pram Bassinet Blanket
description:
'Hungry Caterpillar' Pram Blanket

This pram blanket teams a top fabric of 100% cotton 'Hungry Caterpillar' theme with a coordinating 100% cotton green backing fabric. Blanket also has a lightweight 100% cotton wadding for extra comfort.

name: Girls Butterfly Onsie Tutu Set
description: Size 0-6 months this outfit teams a light pink onsie appliqued with a pretty pink butterfly with a white and light pink tutu. Tutu is completely detachable so onsie can be worn by it self for everyday use or teamed with the tutu for more special occasions.

name: Unisex Hungry Caterpillar Tummy Time Mat
description:
This is not a licensed product. It is however, hand-crafted from licensed fabric. I am not affiliated with or sponsored by Eric Carle Designs. 

This super soft tummy time mat has a top layer of 100% Cotton 'Hungry Caterpillar' themed top fabric with a coordinating back flannelette layer. The mat also has a thick batting to make it super soft and comfy for bub's to practice tummy time skills and it also has two attachments to attach babies favourite toys (toys shown in picture are not included).

name: Custom Birthday Party Set - Onsie, Hat and Bib
description:
Unisex Party hat, bib and onsie set

Make a little prince or princesses birthday that extra bit special with this party hat, bib and onsie set. Great for that wow factor and makes a wonderful photo prop for cake smashes! Price includes 1 x white onsie, 1 x party hat and 1 x bib. Price also includes first name and birthday age on all three items plus your choice of one bow tie / tie or themed applique. 

3 week turnaround time. Available in a onsie from sizes 0000-1 or in a white t-shirt for sizes 2+. Can be customized in your choice your colours, name and number. Please use the contact tab to message us after purchasing with your theme, name and birthday age. An email will be sent within 24 hours with options for you to approve.

name: Dino Standard Newborn to Toddler Bib
description:
Dinosaurs Standard Bib

Milk and Cookie Designs Bibs are designed with reflux and drooling babies in mind. As a mama of two reflux babies (and one incredibly drooly baby) the bibs have been designed for premium absorbency with a stay dry back. 

TLD bibs are made from a top layer of 100% cotton, a middle layer of flannelette and back layer of minky. The two top layers will absorb what needs to be absorbed with the minky ensuring bubs does not have a wet bib against their clothes. TLD bibs also have three snap settings to ensure bibs can be used from the tiny newborn days right up until toddlerhood.
